The game works just fine for me..Thanks a lot re Ellinara!No serial number is needed for those asking..Just skip that part by closin' the window and the game starts automatically installing..The only small problem that occured to me was that the crack file cannot be overwritten to the ".exe" file.So I just erased the ".exe", mounted the iso with "magicdisk" and run the crack file located in the file "Electronic Arts" file inside the Program Files..Have fun guys!
